  <summary>10/27/1987--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to reduce from 28 to 15 percent the maximum income tax rate applicable to the long-term capital gains of individuals. Excludes capital gains from the phaseout affecting personal exemptions and the 15 percent income tax rate.</summary>
